title: Speedy West & Jimmy Bryant - Bear Box & More in FLAC
description:
Torrent includes The Bear Family Box Set "Flamin' Guitars" 
as well as their final CD "For The Last Time," 
all ripped with EAC in secure mode and encoded to flac.
You will also find scans of the covers and discs and scans of the discography in the Bear Family Box Set.
I'm hoping this will encourage others who own Bear Family Boxes
to upload them in lossless sound with scans of the discographies.
I have many other Bear Family Boxes that I'll upload as time permits. Hope you enjoy!
